    InsightFactory
    public class InsightFactory_Impl
extends java.lang.Object
implements InsightFactory
    Implementation of the InsightFactory interface for managing user data within a MongoDB database. Provides methods to query, save, update, and delete user information.
    作者:
    Giuseppe Abrami
